translate portuguese welchq1_90a40ec2:

    # sst "So, I was wondering... why are you in freshman classes as a senior?"
    sst "Então, estava a pensar... porque é que estás nas aulas do primeiro ano sendo do último ano?"

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchq1.rpy:17
translate portuguese welchq1_b0d4142b:

    # sst "Did you wait to do your basics at the end or something? I didn't think they would even let you do that."
    sst "Esperaste para fazer as disciplinas básicas no final ou algo assim? Não achei que te deixassem fazer isso."

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchq1.rpy:18
translate portuguese welchq1_2c8e0198:

    # pc "Sort of. I went to school in Brazil for the last three years."
    pc "Mais ou menos. Estudei no Brasil nos últimos três anos."

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchq1.rpy:20
translate portuguese welchq1_8add5b68:

    # sst "Brazil? Wow!"
    sst "No Brasil? Uau!"

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchq1.rpy:21
translate portuguese welchq1_cfd427d3:

    # sst "I've never heard of anybody going to Brazil for college before."
    sst "Nunca tinha ouvido falar de ninguém que fosse para o Brasil fazer faculdade."

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchq1.rpy:22
translate portuguese welchq1_f1031ec0:

    # sst "Was it fun? Why didn't you finish school there?"
    sst "Foi divertido? Porque é que não terminaste os estudos lá?"

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchq1.rpy:24
translate portuguese welchq1_2101f83b:

    # pc "It was okay."
    pc "Foi mais ou menos."

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchq1.rpy:25
translate portuguese welchq1_a8c03e38:

    # pc "I mostly went to get away from my dad."
    pc "Fui principalmente para fugir do meu pai."

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchq1.rpy:26
translate portuguese welchq1_491bbf21:

    # pc "Then I came back because he went missing."
    pc "Depois voltei porque ele desapareceu."

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchq1.rpy:27
translate portuguese welchq1_7d1ce916:

    # sst "Missing? Really?"
    sst "Desapareceu? A sério?"

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchq1.rpy:28
translate portuguese welchq1_90a4fc00:

    # sst "Whoa..."
    sst "Uau..."

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchq1.rpy:29
translate portuguese welchq1_cd80a08e:

    # pc "Yeah, we're still looking for him."
    pc "Sim, ainda estamos à procura dele."

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchq1.rpy:30
translate portuguese welchq1_5e522282:

    # sst "Oh shit. I think I've seen posters up of him now that I think about it."
    sst "Oh, merda. Acho que já vi cartazes dele, agora que penso nisso."

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchq1.rpy:31
translate portuguese welchq1_b92afc22:

    # sst "He went missing right before the semester started, right?"
    sst "Ele desapareceu mesmo antes do semestre começar, certo?"

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchq1.rpy:32
translate portuguese welchq1_c417e350:

    # pc "Yeah."
    pc "Sim."

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchq1.rpy:34
translate portuguese welchq1_99556521:

    # sst "Fuck, I'm sorry honey. That's awful."
    sst "Foda-se, desculpa, querida. Isso é horrível."

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchq1.rpy:35
translate portuguese welchq1_795ad0a8:

    # sst "I really hope you find him."
    sst "Espero mesmo que o encontres."

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchq1.rpy:36
translate portuguese welchq1_49ac58f6:

    # pc "Thanks, me too."
    pc "Obrigada, eu também."

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchq1.rpy:38
translate portuguese welchq1_d331fa89:

    # sst "If there's ever anything I can do to help, let me know, okay?"
    sst "Se houver alguma coisa que eu possa fazer para ajudar, avisa-me, está bem?"

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchq1.rpy:39
translate portuguese welchq1_562f2c69:

    # pc "Thanks, Ms. Welch. I will."
    pc "Obrigada, Sra. Welch. Vou fazer isso."

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchq1.rpy:40
translate portuguese welchq1_7fdffe26:

    # sst "Nora. Please."
    sst "Nora. Por favor."

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchq1.rpy:41
translate portuguese welchq1_37d515c7:

    # pc "Oh, right. Sorry."
    pc "Ah, certo. Desculpa."

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchq1.rpy:42
translate portuguese welchq1_d46d6d96:

    # sst "It's okay, baby."
